title: Moglea Hand Painted Ornament Holiday Cards—Holly Jolly
description:
A card and a gift all in one!  Hand-painted and foil stamped chipboard ornaments. Two flat pieces fit together to make three-dimensional ornaments. Hand-painted and foil stamped in Iowa. 

  • Boxed set of 6 ornaments with gold and white twine.
  • Card Size:  4.25 in. x 5.5 in. folded
  • Ornament Size:  4 in. x 4 in. flat circles
  • Hand painted in Iowa

*Please note that due to the handmade nature, each product may vary in design/look/appearance.
